('b1-099', 'es', 'seguro', 'safe; sure; insurance', 'No estoy seguro de qué camino tomar.', 'B1'::cefr_level, 'Daily Life', ARRAY['cierto'], '{"note":"Adjective = safe or sure (''estar seguro de'' = to be sure of). As a noun ''el seguro'' = insurance. Adverb ''seguro que...'' = surely.","collocations":["estar seguro de","un lugar seguro"]}'::jsonb),
