('c2-124', 'es', 'acendrado', 'pure, deep-seated (of feelings)', 'Profesaba un acendrado amor por su tierra.', 'C2'::cefr_level, 'Emotions', ARRAY['puro','arraigado'], '{"note":"Pure and deeply held — of feelings or virtues (''acendrado amor/patriotismo''); puro/arraigado are close, acendrado is literary and refined.","collocations":["un acendrado amor","un acendrado patriotismo"]}'::jsonb)
